               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾardǝʾǝt “Book of the Disciples” (The long version beginning
                     with በስመ፡“… ነገር፡ ዘ፲ወ፪አርድእት፡…), (fols. 3ra-40vb l.4) &#xD; II) Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt
                     “Teaching of Mysteries” (fols. 40va l.5-43vb) &#xD; III) Excerpt from Kidān
                     za-nagh “Covenant of the Morning” (ለከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ለገባሬ፡ ኵሉ፡ አምላክ፡ ንሠፍህ፡ አምላክ፡ ንስፍሕ፡
                     ነፍስነ፡ ወስብሐተ፡ ዘነግህ፡…), (fols. 43va-vb) (cp. Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt wa-kidān za-nagh,
                     Addis Abäba 1949 E.C., 13 l.5-14 l.2) &#xD; IV) Anaphora of Our Lady by St
                     Cyriacus of Behnesa (fols. 45ra-53vb), incomplete (MQ, Qǝddāse Māryām, ch. III,
                     §§ 1-82 l.3)&#xD; V) Excerpt from Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (?) (fol.
                     54ra-rb).</summary>

